config.crgltf.opengl_availability.tooltip=Select the OpenGL features available for this mod.\nAuto: Determine by checking the OpenGL version supported by the system.\n\nFull: All OpenGL features can be used; your system must support at least OpenGL 4.3.\n\nGL21_FBO: Follow the minimum OpenGL version requirements; only supports up to OpenGL 2.1+FBO.\n\nUnless there are compatibility issues, setting the option to GL21_FBO will reduce performance.